<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>[0.4.0]<sp/>-<sp/>2023-09-04</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>Added</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/>-<sp/>New<sp/>module<sp/>`ellswift`<sp/>implements<sp/>ElligatorSwift<sp/>encoding<sp/>for<sp/>public<sp/>keys<sp/>and<sp/>x-only<sp/>Diffie-Hellman<sp/>key<sp/>exchange<sp/>for<sp/>them.</highlight></codeline>
