<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/>-<sp/>The<sp/>[paper](https://eprint.iacr.org/2022/759)<sp/>on<sp/>which<sp/>the<sp/>scheme<sp/>is<sp/>based.</highlight></codeline>
